{"tid":273581,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（長文有圖）早排同女神去迪迪尼被人劏到一頸血","createTime":"2017-06-06T16:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T08:39:19.000Z","uid":49163,"like":13,"dislike":188,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9661ee0d60f6de88bf38674ebff1682a0cf3f088","tid":273581,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:07:48.000Z","msg":"話說係女神暗示想去迪迪尼玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就即刻話咁啱有2張飛（589$一張）好肉痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過算啦做兵係要投資下1200啦唯有<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/000043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F000043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=be769f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n11點幾就去到，可能係平日唔多人大陸人佔一半到<br />\n就去左個乜9玩具大本營玩機動遊戲咁，就玩跳樓機先，排隊個陣竟然有條特快隊女神話排特快啦，原來係分開坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴線咁我點保護女神呀！！！算！！！一玩原來係on9 game升上3樓就跌反落黎一兩次咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁無聊囉"},{"pid":"305039b5fafee8928d0bfdcbfdf44622c92f8ce1","tid":273581,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/001005_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F001005_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=60c9d74e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a72ca324ff7f345942788cf1aaed2472ad39fcb0","tid":273581,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"其他game唔多講，玩怪物彈珠仲刺激過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/001117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.n